Title: Zoomex Announces Sponsorship of Ferrari Driver Oliver Bearman and Launches 1 BTC Giveaway to
Intro:
Disclaimer: The text below is a press release that is not part of Cryptonews.com editorial content.

Zoomex, a rapidly growing trading platform, has just announced its sponsorship of Oliver Bearman, a rising British Ferrari driver and member of the Ferrari F1 Driver Academy. Bearman competes with Prema Racing in the FIA Formula 2 and is poised to become one of the sport's brightest young stars.

The Zoomex logo will be prominently displayed on Oliver's car and racing suit, as well as across his social media channels throughout the F2 race calendar. Zoomex and Ollie's team will collaborate closely to expand the sponsorship's global exposure and convey the message that success is achieved through determination and effort.

"We're thrilled to be sponsoring Oliver Bearman as he continues to excel in the world of motorsport," said Amos Z., founder of Zoomex. "With his talent and determination, we know he has what it takes to become one of the sport's biggest stars, and we're proud to be supporting him every step of the way." 

Zoomex 1 BTC Giveaway Campaign.

In addition to sponsoring Bearman, Zoomex has also launched a special giveaway as part of its global launch celebration. All participants will share 1 BTC prize pool, as well as win signed Oliver Signed Wear Merchandise throughout the campaign. The 1 BTC giveaway is available until May 31, 2023. 

 Zoomex is committed to providing traders with the best possible trading experience and the most high-tech blockchain technology, and this giveaway is just one way the platform is rewarding its users. 

How to Participate?.

Users who aim to participate in the 1 BTC giveaway organized by Zoomex should click on the “Register Now” button on the giveaway page and trade once (No threshold for the trading volume) during the campaign period. 

Rewards will be distributed within 10 business days after the campaign ends.

About Zoomex.

Zoomex is a professional cryptocurrency trading platform that upholds the decentralized and anonymous spirit of the blockchain industry. The platform offers a range of financial trading services and is centered around the needs of its customers. 

Unlike other trading platforms, Zoomex requires no KYC for trading, giving its users a safe and warm place for their crypto trading needs. Through its commitment to providing the best possible trading experience, Zoomex has gradually developed into a leader in the cryptocurrency field. 

Currently, the platform supports over 170 trading pairs, covering a wide range of major tokens such as Tether (USDT) and Bitcoin (BTC). Security, customer trust, and innovative thinking are the foundation of Zoomex's existence. Zoomex focuses on the rapidly changing cryptocurrency market, providing high-quality online trading services, and constantly meeting customers’ needs.

Learn More.

To learn more about Zoomex and its latest announcements, you can check the official Zoomex website or follow the crypto project on Twitter, Telegram, KakaoTalk, and Medium.

Intro:
Disclaimer: The text below is a press release that is not part of Cryptonews.com editorial content.

Zoomex, a rapidly growing trading platform, has just announced its sponsorship of Oliver Bearman, a rising British Ferrari driver and member of the Ferrari F1 Driver Academy. Bearman competes with Prema Racing in the FIA Formula 2 and is poised to become one of the sport's brightest young stars.

The Zoomex logo will be prominently displayed on Oliver's car and racing suit, as well as across his social media channels throughout the F2 race calendar. Zoomex and Ollie's team will collaborate closely to expand the sponsorship's global exposure and convey the message that success is achieved through determination and effort.

"We're thrilled to be sponsoring Oliver Bearman as he continues to excel in the world of motorsport," said Amos Z., founder of Zoomex. "With his talent and determination, we know he has what it takes to become one of the sport's biggest stars, and we're proud to be supporting him every step of the way." 

Zoomex 1 BTC Giveaway Campaign.

In addition to sponsoring Bearman, Zoomex has also launched a special giveaway as part of its global launch celebration. All participants will share 1 BTC prize pool, as well as win signed Oliver Signed Wear Merchandise throughout the campaign. The 1 BTC giveaway is available until May 31, 2023. 

 Zoomex is committed to providing traders with the best possible trading experience and the most high-tech blockchain technology, and this giveaway is just one way the platform is rewarding its users. 

How to Participate?.

Users who aim to participate in the 1 BTC giveaway organized by Zoomex should click on the “Register Now” button on the giveaway page and trade once (No threshold for the trading volume) during the campaign period. 

Rewards will be distributed within 10 business days after the campaign ends.

About Zoomex.

Zoomex is a professional cryptocurrency trading platform that upholds the decentralized and anonymous spirit of the blockchain industry. The platform offers a range of financial trading services and is centered around the needs of its customers. 

Unlike other trading platforms, Zoomex requires no KYC for trading, giving its users a safe and warm place for their crypto trading needs. Through its commitment to providing the best possible trading experience, Zoomex has gradually developed into a leader in the cryptocurrency field. 

Currently, the platform supports over 170 trading pairs, covering a wide range of major tokens such as Tether (USDT) and Bitcoin (BTC). Security, customer trust, and innovative thinking are the foundation of Zoomex's existence. Zoomex focuses on the rapidly changing cryptocurrency market, providing high-quality online trading services, and constantly meeting customers’ needs.

Learn More.

【自己紹介】
アポロン
・18歳でパン屋さんに就職
・21歳からブラック企業でウェブマーケティングと鬼営業を学ぶ
・29歳でウェブ広告系の会社へ転職・ベンチャーの立ち上げ経験
・その後独立し、現在はアフィリエイターとしてメディアを運営
・現在はweb3で稼ぐ事が出来るのか？実践中の中年男性

【アポロンの想い】
web1.0時代
2003年に高校を卒業し、僕はパン屋さんに就職しました。
其の時、世の中はホリエモンを中心としたITバブルが巻き起こっていました。
ホームページを作成するだけで数億円を稼ぐ事が出来る世の中。
しかし、僕には全くITスキルを生かしたビジネスをする事はできませんでした。

web2.0時代
その後・・・・・2006年IT系の保険代理店に就職、時代はGoogle一色になろうとしていた。。。しかし、くる日もくる日も僕は保険の営業にあけくれ、Googleを駆使したメディアアフィリエイト の波に乗る事ができなかった。。。。。周囲にはGoogleのSEOを駆使して上場する同い年の経営者も・・・・

Twitter・インスタグラム・AmazonOEM 気付けばweb2.0を駆使した起業家だらけの世の中。。。。。。僕はいつも、始めるのが遅かった・・・それなりに、GoogleのSEOを学び、YouTubeを学び、アフィリエイトで稼げるようにはなった。
でも、もっと早くweb2.0の波に乗りたかった・・・

web3.0時代
そんな中ついに、2021年web3.0が到来・・・・
web2.0では後期でビジネス化してきたけど、web3.0では初期参加者としてこのテクノロジーをどう使うか？考えて実践したい。
web3.0がどんな世界を作るのか？自分の身を持って日本の方々に伝えたい。

そう思い、WEB3 ランドを立ち上げました。
いろんなWeb３関連の事にチャレンジして成長していきますので、暖かく見守っていただけると幸いです。

En la era digital en la que vivimos, el mundo de las finanzas ha experimentado una transformación significativa. Entre los diversos activos disponibles, bitcoin, comúnmente conocido como BTC, ha surgido como una opción popular. 

Pero, ¿es realmente mejor que otros activos? En este artículo, explicaremos en detalle las características de bitcoin y los aspectos clave que lo diferencian de otros activos tradicionales. 

¿Quizás Bitcoin aún no ha tocado fondo? La demanda de la SEC contra Binance sacude la confianza de algunos alcistas de BTC
A medida que desentrañamos las complejidades de este tema, descubriremos si bitcoin es, de hecho, una mejor opción en comparación con otros activos convencionales.

Antes de iniciar es necesario definir qué es bitcoin. Bitcoin, es la primera criptomoneda descentralizada, fue creada en 2009 por una persona o grupo de personas bajo el seudónimo de Satoshi Nakamoto.

Pero, ¿es realmente mejor que otros activos? En este artículo, explicaremos en detalle las características de bitcoin y los aspectos clave que lo diferencian de otros activos tradicionales. 

¿Quizás Bitcoin aún no ha tocado fondo? La demanda de la SEC contra Binance sacude la confianza de algunos alcistas de BTC
A medida que desentrañamos las complejidades de este tema, descubriremos si bitcoin es, de hecho, una mejor opción en comparación con otros activos convencionales.

Antes de iniciar es necesario definir qué es bitcoin. Bitcoin, es la primera criptomoneda descentralizada, fue creada en 2009 por una persona o grupo de personas bajo el seudónimo de Satoshi Nakamoto.

10代はスポーツに打ち込み、国体、インターハイ等の全国大会に毎年出場する。しかし、大学進学に失敗したことを機に将来を失望。あらゆるギャンブル等で失敗を重ね、ダメ人間生活を送っていた。

学歴無し、地頭悪い、根性無し、一歩がなかなか踏み出せなかった僕でも、毎日少しずつ継続していくことで稼げるようになったのですから。
まだまだ遅くはないです。いつからでもやり直せます！
単なる仮想通貨情報だけでなく、僕の人生観も読み取っていただけたら幸甚です。
